theorem interior_inter_frontier_eq_empty {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    interior A ∩ frontier A = (∅ : Set X) := by
  simpa [frontier_eq_closure_diff_interior]
    using (Set.inter_diff_self (interior A) (closure A))

theorem interior_subset_of_subset_open {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (hAB : A ⊆ B) (hB : IsOpen B) :
    interior A ⊆ B := by
  intro x hxIntA
  exact hAB (interior_subset hxIntA)
